data.title: Railway model 1/150 Shin-Keisei 80000 Type 6-Pair Set [A1222]
data.meta_description:
Product Description ■ Gentle Pink Shin-Keisei 80000!
[Actual car]
Keisei 3100 made its debut on October 26, 2019 as a Access express car for Narita Sky Access Line.
The exterior design is based on orange, which is the guide color for Keisei Line, in order to prevent passengers from getting on the wrong train.
Images of of Sky ACCESS access, are drawn on the car body as an accent in order to prevent mistaken boarding with airports.
Made by Nippon Sharyo Co., Ltd. and General Rolling Stock Manufacturing Co., Ltd., and the 3151 train sets made by Nippon Sharyo Co., Ltd. have a stainless steel decorative plate on the spot welding Atobe at the body hem.
The Shin-Keisei 80000 made its debut in December 2019. It was developed jointly with Keisei Electric Railway 3100.
The coloring is made with a Gentle pink line on the upper part, so that the Shin-Keisei corporate color can be seen from the surrounding even when the train runs on an elevated section.
The shape of the handrail at the front of the crew room door is different from that of the Keisei 3100.
Equipped with a power unit with a flywheel.
Lighting the headlights, tail lights, and front indicators.
Reproducing the handrails under the crew door with a unique shape (with an ON / OFF switch).
Made a front car roof different from that of the Micro Ace 3100.
Reproducing the high-back sheet that can be seen through the windows.
Printing the same design as the actual car through the doors.
[Product details]
Scale : 1/150 9 mm (N gauge)
Product form : Painted, completed product
Motor : Yes (power unit with flywheel)
Accessories : Destination seal
* The price of this product may be changed because it is pre-paid. Please understand in advance. 80000 80000 3100 Shin-Keisei Shin-Keisei Gentle

[Actual car]

Keisei 3100 made its debut on October 26, 2019 as a Access express car for Narita Sky Access Line.

Images of of Sky ACCESS access, are drawn on the car body as an accent in order to prevent mistaken boarding with airports.

Made by Nippon Sharyo Co., Ltd. and General Rolling Stock Manufacturing Co., Ltd., and the 3151 train sets made by Nippon Sharyo Co., Ltd. have a stainless steel decorative plate on the spot welding Atobe at the body hem.

The Shin-Keisei 80000 made its debut in December 2019. It was developed jointly with Keisei Electric Railway 3100.

The coloring is made with a Gentle pink line on the upper part, so that the Shin-Keisei corporate color can be seen from the surrounding even when the train runs on an elevated section.

The shape of the handrail at the front of the crew room door is different from that of the Keisei 3100.

Equipped with a power unit with a flywheel.

Lighting the headlights, tail lights, and front indicators.

Made a front car roof different from that of the Micro Ace 3100.

Reproducing the high-back sheet that can be seen through the windows.

Printing the same design as the actual car through the doors.

[Product details]
